snippet.title: Boiling Bolt - Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
Help us to make Boiling Bolt even crazier and awesome.
We are doing an Itch.io refinery : https://plug-in-digital-label.itch.io/boiling-bolt

Watch the official announcement teaser for Boiling Bolt available on PC later this year.

Boiling Bolt is coming to PC & Mac in 2016!
Follow us on :
*** Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/BoilingBolt
*** Twitter - https://twitter.com/BoilingBolt
*** IndieDB : http://www.indiedb.com/games/boilingbolt
And don't hesitate to subscribe to our channel to receive latest video update ;)
